messages.message: Hey team. They are a couple of tickets for processing password protected documents in JIRA, but I think they are all for the legacy platform. Should we create a new one or update the previous tickets ?
Were we able to test if using runtime configs works for this purpose? I think that's where the last thread (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05BJCNKZAM/p1742328222843889) left off cc @david.lee
